public class RecvEventMultiplayerClientStarted
extends RecvEvent

The RecvEventMultiplayerClientStarted structure is sent to a client when they have successfully joined a multi-player race. This event is not transmitted to the host of the session, only to the client that has joined in. To receive these events, refer to the SimConnect_SubscribeToSystemEvent function.
